                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Curacao</placeName>\n                <date>13 February 1858</date>—</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Reverend Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">With none of your to reply too I. <sic>reffer</sic>.<lb/> to my last\n                of the <date>16 December</date> Ulto which I hope have rea,,<lb/>ched you\n                    <sic>safed</sic> together with $68, <sic>remetted</sic> to the of\n                    <persName>Messrs<lb/> Dovale &amp; Co.</persName>\n                <placeName>N/Y.</placeName> I have this pleasure again to day of<lb/> sending you to\n                the care of said Gentlemen forty dollars<lb/> which I have collected from a few\n                friends as donation<lb/> for the new <sic>Sinagoge</sic>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Beth El</hi> of your place, this<lb/> sum have not been\n                    <sic>remetted</sic> before, because I have<lb/> been absent from home for some\n                times; donation sh,,<lb/>ould,, have been liberal by every members here, if it\n                was<lb/> not for so many subscription, donation, and loans,<lb/> which were given\n                during last year, but any how I<lb/> hope this will be accepted. The exhibition I\n                mention,,<lb/>eted you in my last Shall be upon on the <date>19 April</date><lb/>\n                next, the benefit of the same shall be <sic>destributed</sic><lb/> between the three\n                communities, Israelites, Protestant,<lb/> and Catholics; a commission of directors\n                is appointed <persName>Rev:<lb/> Choemaceiro</persName> is chosen as President,\n                    <persName>Mr Mehyer</persName> Pro,,<lb/>testant minister vice P. <persName>Mr\n                    Kickens</persName> Catholic mi,,<lb/>nister <sic>Serc</sic>.; and <persName>Mr\n                    D. Senior Jr</persName> Treasurer this plan<lb/> has been invented by <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Haham</hi>; I shall have the<lb/> pleasure of communicate you\n                the result of it<lb/> afterwards; <sic>Pleace</sic> to give this to your\n                readers—</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I am very truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B. de Cafferes Jr</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3d50gh7b/canvas/p1"
                }
